node.text: We talk about experimenting, being and embracing YOU as your secret weapon and how there is no one set path. node.text: @chrisellelim, creative, co-founder of @bumoparent and mama of 2 chat about how shortcuts may seem shiny and sparkling but they often let us down + how taking the time to get to your destination gives you experience and the joy of doing it! Also if you are in LA, head over and join @bumoparent which is THE BEST RESOURCE for working parents. If you want your child educated and cared for and need a place to call home, this is it. Buy my book wherever books are sold and email me the receipt to fearless@rebeccaminkoff.com to attend to my incredible launch event June 15th!

node.title: Fearless Rule #11 Skip the short cuts, no one is timing you with @chriselle

node.text: @mrsbrittanyhennessy and I talk about all things CHANGE! Change can be scary and painful but you won’t ever know if you are on the right path until you jump (with parachute). @mrsbrittanyhennessy has an incredible book, Influencer out as well if getting into the field has always been a dream and helps tons of women all over the world to understand, use and thrive off their personal brand. Don’t forget to preorder my book at readfearless.com and get access to all sorts of goodies like a site credit, my masterclass, audio book and more! Also grab her book too and start your journey of becoming an #influencer.

node.title: Fearless, Rule #10 Change things up with author @mrsbrittanyhennessy

node.text: Join @babba and I as we chat about rule #9, how to create a network and how networking in your career doesn’t have to be about social climbing. She shares an example of how networking with your peers is more valuable than the most important person in the room and how it can lead to more opportunities. She also shares a #fearless moment when she was scared but pursued it anyway. Support her by heading over to @myceremonia , the product is incredible for hair! Lastly, preorder my book @ readfearless.com and email me fearless@rebeccaminkoff.com your receipt to unlock a ton of goodies from supporting my book!

node.title: Fearless Rule #9 Create Two Way Streets with @myceremonia founder @babba

node.text: Join us as we dive into Rule #6, Love it and leave it, be okay with walking away.  Cass and I talk about how challenging it can be to start a company and when to walk away from things that are not working. Don’t forget to PRE-order @ readfearless.com and email me fearless@rebeccaminkoff.com to unlock all the goodies like $25 Rm gift card, my masterclass, and so much more!

node.text: For NYFW, we collaborated with @magnumicecream, on a custom-designed Ice Cream Cart as a continuation of our love letter to NYC, inspired by my new collection. We started our day on the streets of SoHo, handing out ice cream bars and custom bar design kits to fans and shoppers, and ended the day at my “I Love New York” Event offering all guests a stylish treat to complement their looks. I even snuck a bar (or two!) throughout the day – so good! #MagnumMoments #MagnumPartner

node.text: Today we remember all of those who lost their lives and loved ones. A day that will never be forgotten. New York is one of the most resilient cities in the world and we have weathered many storms. In honor of that and in order to rebuild, we are donating all the proceeds from the sale of our NFTS to a grant for female founders impacted during the pandemic in NYC. Administered by @thefemalefoundercollective, this grant will help rebuild, support and uplift the hardest hit WOBs and get them back on their feet. We can all do something to support and get this city back on its feet, one person at a time like we did 20 years ago.
